{"tid":1506142,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"麻煩大家幫手report呢個channel","createTime":"2019-08-25T17:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T18:43:25.000Z","uid":78267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c983985b22335c487fe085ebf0e10a9ed520e8e2","tid":1506142,"uid":78267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:19:58.000Z","msg":"唔知開咩台好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個channel淨係focus係勇武巴絲嘅行為<br />\n話示威者係畜牲係曱甴 甚至會搶劫<br />\n不停係到屌記者 話有示威者扮記者打警察<br />\n淨係讚tvb記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話佢夠中立<br />\n對警察濫權視而不見仲堅稱自己客觀<br />\n仲以為示威者有大台係背後控制<br />\n屋企兩老日日睇仲話講得好<br />\n我實在睇唔過眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麻煩各位幫幫手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">天佑香港</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ihD1bzf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FihD1bzf.png&h=22c2e9f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xjC6harCVFo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxjC6harCVFo&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxqVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=3b5cede3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xjC6harCVFo</a>"},{"pid":"a09ae428885b49ff240e9134d09121e4144b7c27","tid":1506142,"uid":78267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:23:09.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"c2c2cd25a29b1677b8995c2a14f5a554c8b02242","tid":1506142,"uid":78267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:23:25.000Z","msg":"大大力再推"},{"pid":"e26d1533a0311d5842cfb20977929346b0cdd38e","tid":1506142,"uid":78267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:23:39.000Z","msg":"輕輕力又推"},{"pid":"2c742f8e10572bf4b9bfb8a4a0d1cecfa6c5c3bd","tid":1506142,"uid":78267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:23:50.000Z","msg":"細細力又推"},{"pid":"c559c21f476accc7aa4d209ddf4b4dd18b4b087